Retrieve COVID-19 data for states/provinces in a country or countries

Source: R/getAdmn1ByCountry.R
getAdmn1ByCountry.Rd

Retrieve up-to-date COVID-19 data from outbreak.info for all states/provinces in one or more countries.

getAdmn1ByCountry(countries, ...)

Arguments

countries:

vector or list of country name(s)

Value

dataframe

Examples

getAdmn1ByCountry("India")
